snippet.title: Diablo III: Reaper of Souls Feature Trailer
snippet.description:
Malthael, the Angel of Death, beckons. Will you answer his call? http://diablo3.com/ReaperOfSouls 

Premiering at BlizzCon 2013, catch a glimpse at Diablo III's first expansion, Reaper of Souls, in our all-new feature trailer.

Go anywhere and slay anything in Adventure Mode; roam the land with total freedom using fully unlocked waypoints to seamlessly journey from one act to another. Explore endlessly with Bounties and Nephalem Rifts, and be rewarded handsomely for your efforts. Join other brave nephalem on the battlefield with our new Clans and Groups social features. Customize the power and look of your equipment with an all-new artisan, the Mystic. And expand your hero's power with a completely revamped Paragon level system.

Can't get enough? Learn more at: http://www.diablo3.com
